title: Rush - Snakes and Arrows LIVE [320k MP3]
description:
Snakes & Arrows Live is a live double CD and DVD by Canadian band Rush, released on April 14, 2008 in the UK and on April 15, 2008 around the world. The material was taken from two performances during the first leg of the Snakes & Arrows Tour, recorded at the Ahoy Arena in Rotterdam, Netherlands on October 16 and 17, 2007. This is the first of the band's live albums since the Grace Under Pressure Tour to highlight one studio work specifically, with nine of the 27 tracks drawn from Snakes & Arrows. A DVD and Blu-ray version of this album was released on November 24, 2008.
